import json

nodevalue = r"""$addhashtocase"""
jsondata = json.loads(nodevalue)

# Access the first element of the list and then extract _id
_id = jsondata[0]["body"][0]["_id"]

# Get the first 9 characters of _id
first_9_chars = _id[:10]

# Print the first 9 characters
print(first_9_chars)
